      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Route by Event Kind\n\nRoutes each item to one of 4 lanes: opened, closed, reopened + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Handle 'opened' → Google Sheets · ②→ Handle 'closed' → Forward API · ③→ Handle 'reopened' → Forward API · ④→ Log Unrecognized Kind",
